{"serial": "43044", "department_serial": 41, "code": "IMA004", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Supply chain Management in E-Commerce", "ch": "電子商務供應鏈管理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "授課教師：陳仲儼老師、何靖遠老師"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Ho, Chin-Yuan", "Chen, Chung-Yang"], "ch": ["何靖遠", "陳仲儼"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 6, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "404"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士在職專班", "en": "Master Programme (Adult Learning)"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 31, "remark": {"ch": "授課教師：陳仲儼老師、何靖遠老師", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在介紹各種供應鏈的管理決策使學生具備批判思考和解決問題的能力。實務案例研討使學生可以交叉驗證供應鏈管理的理論和實務。供應鏈管理(SCM)所關切的是企業如何透過流程整合和伙伴間的協同合作，藉助資訊科技以協調供應鏈各環節的供給和需求，目的在降低供應鏈執行的成本，提升供應鏈的回應能力。", "en": "“This course is to introduce various decision making in supply chain management (SCM) to equip students with critical thinking and problem-solving capabilities. Real SCM cases will be studied to cross-examine SCM theories and practices. SCM concerns how a business, through process integration and collaboration with partners in the supply chain (SC), coordinate the supply and demand in various stages of the SC with the help of information technology, in order to reduce SC’s execution cost and enhance SC’s responsiveness.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "SCM將持續成為企業電子化的重要課題。本課程會介紹供應鏈中各層級的決策問題及其解決方案，使學生具備解決問題的實作能力。課程內容包括供應鏈的策略適配和供應鏈設計與規劃的方法和技術。具體地說，就是在既定的供應鏈策略下，如何運用設施、存貨、運輸、資訊、採購和定價等影響供應鏈績效的驅動因子，使供應鏈的績效最佳化。試算表方法將會用來研討教學案例，實務案例報告可以深入瞭解業者所面臨的供應鏈管理問題和作法。個人實務作業以單一案例貫穿課程主題，可以成為珍貴的學習歷程檔案。", "en": "SCM will continuously be an essential lesson for e-Business. Subjects include achieving strategic fit of a SC and methodologies and technologies for the design and planning of SC’s.  Given the chosen SC strategy, SC performance drivers, such as facility, inventory, transportation, information, sourcing, and pricing should be deployed to optimize the SC performance.  Spreadsheets approach will be used to study teaching and real cases. Both group report and individual report of real SCM cases are required."}, "textbook": {"ch": "“1.供應鏈管理─策略、規劃與作業，第七版，Sunil Chopra，Pearson Education Limited 2019. 2.目標，Goldratt, E. M.，齊若蘭譯，1996，天下文化“", "en": "“1. Supply Chain Management—Strategy, Planning, and Operation, 7th ed., Sunil Chopra, Pearson Education Limited 2019.\n2. The Goal，Goldratt, E. M.，齊若蘭譯，1996，天下文化“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "20", "en": "20"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“Individual Assignment (個人作業) 35％ Group Paper/Theses Writing (分組報告) 35％ Individual/Group Presentation (專題發表) 20％ Class Participation (出席率) 10％“", "en": "“Individual Assignment (個人作業) 35％\nGroup Paper/Theses Writing (分組報告) 35％\nIndividual/Group Presentation (專題發表) 20％\nClass Participation (出席率) 10％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "另行約定", "en": "By appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理", "en": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "社會責任", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies"